cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "wickra-strategy-ci"
abstract: >-
  A test runner for trading strategies built on the Wickra backtest engine:
  golden-pins a strategy's BacktestReport, catches regressions in CI, and
  property-tests strategies against fuzzed market data. The core is a data-driven
  library exposed as a JSON-over-C-ABI API in ten languages, with a reference CLI
  and a reusable composite GitHub Action.
type: software
authors:
